caption.title: Simulated intervention results by the combination of all the other three actions discussed in this work.
caption.p:
A and B present the number of cases and the cumulative number of infect people, respectively. The solid blue line is the simulation without intervention ω, ω
o , ϵ = 0.0. The dashed red line presents the data for ω, ω
o , ϵ = 0.25, and the dotted yellow shows the data for ω, ω
